I like Popeye's, but this location is the absolute worst-- every time I go in, the people look at me like "yeah, what do you want?" and then proceed to screw up my order half the time or even forget about my order entirely.  There's an entirely new batch of workers just about every month, and they always seem confused and poorly trained.  Last time I was in there, I asked for the Tuesday Special, and the woman didn't even bother to tell me they didn't have that deal anymore and charged me full price.  And they always act like "Here's your chicken, now get out" like they can't wait to clock out.  If you want a decent Popeye's, the one on Harlem/Higgins is far better managed.
